      "privateNotes": "",
      "publicNotes": "<p><strong>Role:</strong> the garrison that never went off duty — Kazavon's <strong>minotaur</strong> mercenaries (kept intruders out and his own troops <em>in</em>), slain by Mandraivus and risen as horned skeletal champions. Posted at B3 (2 per room), B17 (5), C1 (4), C13 (1), D2 (2 per turret), E3 (3, advanced); <strong>12 more</strong> walk patrol routes as wanderers. They raise alarms by dying.</p>",
